Input domain information

Runtime (2 seconds), finished at Fri Jul 15 09:33:36 2022 (Asia/Shanghai).

An interactive table of user-input domains, with 1st column Identifier for domain identifiers, 2nd column Level for domain level, and 3rd column Description for domain description. Domains are hyperlinked to the domain-specific information page (see the column Identifier).

Enriched ontology terms

An interactive table for enriched ontology terms. Each enriched term (the columns Ontology, Term ID and Term Name) has the enrichment z-score (the column Z-score), the enrichment significant level (the column FDR), the number of overlapped member domains (the column Num) and the overlapped member list (the column Members). Ontology terms are hyperlinked to the term-specific information page (see the column Term ID).

Dotplot of enriched ontology terms

A dotplot for enriched ontology terms (FDR < 0.05) identified according to Fishers exact test. Also provided is an editable PDF file for download.
